@NonNullByDefault

Package com.io7m.jstructural.xom

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SDocumentXHTMLWriter
    The interface supported by document writers.
    SDocumentXHTMLWriterCallbacks
    A set of callbacks allowing for document customisation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SDocumentParser
    A document parser that uses XOM to process documents.
    SDocumentSerializer
    Serialization functions that use XOM to serialize document elements to XML.
    SDocumentXHTMLWriterMulti
    An XHTML writer that produces XHTML 1.0 Strict documents, creating new pages on parts and sections.
    SDocumentXHTMLWriterSingle
    An XHTML writer that produces XHTML 1.0 Strict documents, as a single page.
    SXHTML
    XHTML utility functions.
